<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('partials/fonts') %>
    <title>About Us - RideMate</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>

<body class="font-[Inter]">

    <div class="bg-gray-100 min-h-screen px-4 pt-6 pb-12">
        <%- include('homePartials/profile') %>
        <%- include('homePartials/menu') %>

        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#6d74fc] mb-6">
                About <span class="text-gray-800">RideMate</span>
            </h1>

            <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                    Welcome to <strong class="text-[#6d74fc]">RideMate</strong>, the premier real-time ride-sharing platform designed exclusively for university students and daily commuters.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Our mission is simple: to make commuting more affordable, environmentally friendly, and socially connected. Whether you're a driver looking to split gas costs or a passenger looking for a convenient lift, RideMate connects you instantly with people heading your way.
                </p>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-8 mb-8">
                    <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-blue-100">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#6d74fc] text-xl mb-3 flex items-center">
                            <span class="text-2xl mr-2">🌍</span> Eco-Friendly
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm">By sharing rides, we actively reduce the number of vehicles on the road, lowering our collective carbon footprint and contributing to a greener campus environment.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-blue-100">
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-[#6d74fc] text-xl mb-3 flex items-center">
                            <span class="text-2xl mr-2">💸</span> Cost-Effective
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm">Why pay full price for daily travel? RideMate allows students to split fuel costs fairly, making education and commuting vastly more affordable for everyone.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">How It Works</h2>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-3">
                    <li><strong>Offer a Ride:</strong> Drivers can easily publish a ride by entering their starting point, destination, and available seats.</li>
                    <li><strong>Find a Ride:</strong> Passengers can search for rides matching their route and request a seat in real-time.</li>
                    <li><strong>Live Updates:</strong> Powered by WebSockets, you get instant notifications when someone joins your ride or if a ride is completed.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100 text-center">
                <p class="text-gray-500 italic">Built with passion by Darshan Varpe</p>
                <a href="/home" class="inline-block mt-4 bg-[#6d74fc] hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-medium px-6 py-2 rounded-full transition-colors">
                    Back to Dashboard
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/flowbite@2.5.2/dist/flowbite.min.js"></script>
</html>
